OL,3,CExecutive accused of 'Polyfilla
OL,4,Cpolitics' over health pay
OL,6,FThe leader of Stormont's opposition
OL,7,Fhas accused the Executive of
OL,8,F'Polyfilla politics' in the way it has
OL,9,Fawarded pay parity to healthcare
OL,10,Fworkers in Northern Ireland.
OL,12,FOn Thursday, the Stormont Executive
OL,13,Fapproved on a #100m overspend in the
OL,14,Fhealth budget - that money has come
OL,15,Ffrom next year's funding pot.
OL,17,F"This is chaotic," said SDLP MLA
OL,18,FMatthew O'Toole.
