OL,4,Cpolitics' over health pay
OL,6,F"Pay is fundamental to the delivery of
OL,7,Fpublic services, so it is right that
OL,8,Fwe do look at pay as something that
OL,9,Fhas to be dealt with and has to be
OL,10,Fdealt with properly for the
OL,11,Fworkforce," said John Patrick Clayton
OL,12,Ffrom the union.
OL,14,F"But of course it is a matter of
OL,15,Fconcern that that this is having to be
OL,16,Fdone.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
