OL,6,F"And it goes to that wider discussion,
OL,7,FI think that we need to have about how
OL,8,Fwe make sure that pay is properly
OL,9,Fbudgeted for in future years, and we
OL,10,Fdon't find ourselves in these sorts of
OL,11,Fpositions where we're having to get
OL,12,Fvery, very deep into the financial
OL,13,Fyear before we get any clarity about
OL,14,Fwhat funding is actually available."
OL,16,FUTV was told the health minister was
OL,17,Fnot available for interview today.
