OL,6,FIn his statement on Thursday, Mike
OL,7,FNesbitt said healthcare workers in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland are to receive a pay
OL,9,Fuplift that will restore parity with
OL,10,Fthe rest of the UK.
OL,12,FThe announcement delivers uplifts as
OL,13,Frecommended by pay review bodies in
OL,14,FApril.
OL,16,FNurses had warned of imminent strike
OL,17,Faction if a 3.6% increase recommended
OL,18,Fby the independent Pay Review Body was
OL,19,Fnot met.
