OL,4,Cpolitics' over health pay
OL,6,FMr Nesbitt said: "The Executive has
OL,7,Ftoday given me approval to deliver pay
OL,8,Fparity for health service staff, which
OL,9,Fwas our original intention and what
OL,10,Funions and professional bodies have
OL,11,Fbeen asking for and is their right.
OL,13,F"This would restore pay parity with
OL,14,Fthe percentage uplifts as recommended
OL,15,Fby pay review bodies being back dated
OL,16,Fin full to 1 April 2025.
OL,18,F"I would expect our HSC workforce to
OL,19,Freceive their uplift and back pay in
OL,20,Ftheir February 2026 pay packets."
