OL,6,FThe minister said: "In addition, and
OL,7,Fto ensure that issue of late payment
OL,8,Fof pay awards will never happen again,
OL,9,FI can confirm that as Health Minister
OL,10,FI am committed to ensuring future pay
OL,11,Fawards are prioritised in my budget
OL,12,Fallocation at the start of the
OL,13,Ffinancial year and adjusted as
OL,14,Fnecessary to ensure parity."
